<br>
Nice first post. I would be impressed with 1200ac/3700hp at that level if you want to talk uber.<br>
<br>
Anyway to the original poster, your AC is just fine. Keep in mind that you get 3ac for ever point of defense and you have a ways to go to the cap. Level 60 cap is 252 and at level 54 you should have around 230. That probably translates to another 66AC or so just for maxing your defense. I would start focusing on HP gear as much as you can. Most armor that is an upgrade for you should have decent AC anyway so try to get anything with HP or STA or both if possible.<br>
<br>
Some nice items that shouldn't break the bank:<br>
<br>
Cloak of the maelstorm (11ac 6sta 55hp)<br>
2x black saphire electrum earrings (2ac 35hp)<br>
crystal spider eyes (8ac 35hp)<br>
clattering bone necklace (8ac 6str 6sta 30hp)<br>
any of the dragonwing shoulders (worked 11ac 25hp up to matchless 15ac 65hp)<br>
idol of the thorned (10ac 7str 10sta)<br>
<br>
If you went with the lowest dragon wing shoulders, these items would give you a net result of -20ac -5str but in return you get +19sta +165hp. The net hp gain would be 267 when you factor in hp from sta. Yes the -20ac seems like it will suck, but you will get most of that ac back when you max defense in level 55. Or, once you upgrade you BP you will have the ac back and then some so the additional 267hp is a really good trade. If you made the changes today your stats would be around 2723hp and 1077ac. If you got ahold of a matchless dragonwing mantle you would end up at 2763hp and 1083ac.<br>
<br>
You should also consider investing in a stack of halas meat pies and grobb liquidized meat. These stats food give you a little over 100hp when you use them. <p><div align="center" style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial"><img src="http://www.bfdesigns.net/eq/wandor_sig.jpg"><br><a target="_blank" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6103"><b>Wandor</b></a> | <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6102" target="_blank"><b>Moordian</b></a> | <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=353608" target="_blank"><b>Wandorfu</b></a><br><a target="_blank" href="http://www.exarch.net/"><b>Fusion of Flame</b></a></div></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A> at: 9/15/02 11:51:27 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior>The Steel Warrior</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker>The Bunker</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.steelwarrior.org">The Steel Warrior website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.9.5.6<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

